com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.plugins.geojson

Class GeoJsonPlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.plugins.geojson.GeoJsonPlugin
  • Deprecated. 
    this plugin has been deprecated and will no longer be supported. Similar functionality is built into Runtime Styling found inside the Map SDK.

    @Deprecated
public class GeoJsonPlugin
extends Object
    The GeoJson plugin enables you to easily load GeoJSON data into your project from a URL, an asset file, or path.

    using GeoJsonPluginBuilder class for building GeoJsonPlugin with specific variables with Context with MapboxMap and one the file's name, the file's path, or a URL that points to a GeoJSON file.

      • GeoJsonPlugin

        @Deprecated
public GeoJsonPlugin(Context context,
                                 com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.maps.MapboxMap map,
                                 String fileName,
                                 String filePath,
                                 String url,
                                 OnLoadingGeoJsonListener loadFilePath,
                                 OnLoadingGeoJsonListener loadFileAssets,
                                 OnLoadingGeoJsonListener loadURL,
                                 int fillColor,
                                 int stockColor,
                                 int width,
                                 boolean isRandomFillColor,
                                 boolean isRandomStockColor,
                                 OnMarkerEventListener markerEventListener)
        Deprecated. this plugin has been deprecated and will no longer be supported. Similar functionality is built into Runtime Styling found inside the Map SDK.
        Parameters:
        context - the context of parent activity
        map - the MapboxMap to apply elements to
        fileName - the file name that located in the Assets folder
        filePath - the path of file located on the device
        url - the URL of the GeoJSON file
        loadFilePath - the instance of onLoadingGeoJsonListener used for detecting when the file is loaded via a certain path
        loadFileAssets - the instance of onLoadingGeoJsonListener used for detecting when the file is located in the assets folder
        loadURL - the instance of onLoadingGeoJsonListener used for detecting when the file is loaded via specific URL
        fillColor - the fill color of polygons that are drawn on the map
        stockColor - the stock color of polygons and polylines that are drawn on the map
        width - the width of the polyline
        isRandomFillColor - if true, the fill color will be random
        isRandomStockColor - if true, the stock color will be random
        markerEventListener - the instance of OnMarkerEventListener used to detect a marker click event
